{"tid":1885987,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯黑帝共享勞倫斯體育獎","createTime":"2020-02-18T16:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:51:28.000Z","uid":78243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d21c3c05f728b7336fb76c99d6f657477ce23de2","tid":1885987,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】球王美斯與F1「黑帝」咸美頓同獲頒2019年勞倫斯體育獎的男子最佳運動員。<br />\n<br />\n32歲的美斯（Lionel Messi）成為這獎項設立20年以來，首位獲得最佳男子運動員大獎的足球員，這位巴塞隆拿巨星透過視像透露得獎感受：「我為成為首位以隊際運動員身份獲獎的人感到榮幸。」美斯的宿敵基斯坦奴朗拿度過去也曾競逐這個獎項，但未能如願。<br />\n<br />\n至於35歲的F1車手咸美頓去年6奪總冠軍，得獎並不令人意外。美國體手操名將比爾絲則當選女子最佳運動員。贏得去年欖球世界盃的南非，力壓歐聯盟主利物浦及贏得女子世界盃冠軍的美國隊，贏得年度最佳球隊殊榮。<br />\n<br />\n至於前NBA名將魯域斯基獲頒終身成就獎。"},{"pid":"7b7035a5e005e58972de6621e991b535b3835b29","tid":1885987,"uid":90515,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"無門前等餵嘅都係垃圾"},{"pid":"3510f93d5fb551d85157237856d4fb62ef5f61b4","tid":1885987,"uid":78243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"唔過兩頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e098c717077a931fe34b246e5a1b31e9a5f2b3","tid":1885987,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"655cebb39e47759972d2047faaa41193e702256a","tid":1885987,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54e098c717077a931fe34b246e5a1b31e9a5f2b3","tid":1885987,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"推唔旭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f53c9242ef51c89b2f366347f3a8c4eaec47a6","tid":1885987,"uid":90515,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"希望朗迷回應下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833e2984c0497fbf49e6002f7fd5263f2e5cee32","tid":